data.description: You'll love this charming, 1.5-story home with spectacular space for entertaining. Open 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home with 2 additional half baths.  Upstairs is flex space ready for home entertainment system, game room, whatever you can imagine.  Don't forget Spacious 2-stall garage.  This home gives you over 2750 sqft of generous space to move about(without losing that quaint, cozy atmosphere when it's time to cuddle up with a good book). Situated in a friendly community with an award-winning school system in San Antonio. Minutes away from SeaWorld, 1604, & 23 minutes from the River Walk. Or stay home & enjoy the covered patio w/ nice extended deck and nice yard.
